Why this Project:
Directly aligned with current government and civic-tech trends like AI-powered grievance redressal
(CPGRAMS, state-level pilots, AI NCH, IGMS).
‚Ä¢ Emphasizes human-in-loop, ethical AI and real multi-layer governance logic, which is rare in
typical student projects.
